resources.string:
①.normal(selectable): Enabled for select the device for provision operation;
②.normal(auto): Enabled for scanning, provisioning and key-binding one by one automatically;
③.remote provision: If remote provision enabled, provision process will be:
	1. Scan for an unprovisioned device, connect and provision;
	2. Keep the connection state, send scan command to the device;
	3. Some remote devices info will be upload;
	4. Check and do provision one by one.
④.fast provision: Telink private provision profile, scan and setting device by direct connected mesh device.

If remote provision enabled, provision process will be:

 1. Scan for an unprovisioned device, connect and provision;

 2. Keep the connection state, send scan command to the device;

 3. Some remote devices info will be upload;

 4. Check and do provision one by one;
